# Gmail API Configuration
#
# Setup instructions:
# 1. Go to Google Cloud Console: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a new project or select existing
# 3. Enable Gmail API for the project
# 4. Go to APIs & Services > Credentials
# 5. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Desktop application type)
# 6. Download credentials.json
# 7. Place credentials.json at: ~/.config/the-cinema-bandit/credentials.json
#
# OAuth Consent Screen:
# - Add scope: https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.send
# - Add your email as test user (for development)
#
# First run will open browser for OAuth consent
# Token will be saved at: ~/.config/the-cinema-bandit/gmail-token.json
